title: Drop Beat Dad
description: Steven helps Sour Cream put on a show, even though Sour Cream's stepdad doesn't approve of DJs.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Tripped Up/Power Tripp
description: Tripped Up: Dan and Wynton stumble on both a possible hidden location of the Mind Core Cell and Colonel Tripp who wants the energy source for himself./Power Tripp: After a falling out with Dan, Wynton is mind-controlled by Tripp who stages an attack to ignite a war between Brawlers and the Military.

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Shun Shine/Ronin Son
description: Shun Shine: The AO want to evolve their Bakugan like Dan did with Drago but only Shun finds a way by tapping into the energy of the Mind Core Cell./Ronin Son: When Shun's cousin Masato Kazami claims Hydorous as his intellectual property the AO must battle to keep their friend by their side.

title: Questing For Quests
description: Realizing they have gone soft, the ninja search for a quest to reignite their Spinjitzu training. Unfortunately, NINJAGO City is enjoying a period of rare tranquility.

title: El Atajo
description: Un día inusualmente caluroso en el Arroyo derrite todos los helados de Kit, así que Craig la ayuda a encontrar un atajo para llegar a su proveedor de bocadillos helados antes de que todos los demás se derritan.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Charmed, I'm Sure
description: Still stranded on the monster planet Anur Transyl, Ben and Rook reluctantly team up with Charmcaster to take on Zs' Skayr.

title: I Don't Like You
description: Ben and Gwen's social media battle with Kevin 11 quickly escalates into an all-out war in real life.

title: Pelea de Vapor en el Corral
#GatoCallejero Parte 1
description: Cuando Zee Zatara se da cuenta de que Lex Luthor desenterró un libro mágico que tiene el poder de predecir el futuro, las chicas le piden ayuda a Gatúbela para robárselo antes de que Lex comprenda lo que tiene en su poder. Pero puede que ya sea demasiado tarde...
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Where's Pocoyo?
description: Pocoyo plays hide and seek with us. Can you find him?

title: #AllyCat Part 1
description: When Zee Zatara realizes Lex Luthor has unearthed a magical book with the power to tell the future, the girls reluctantly enlist Catwoman to help them steal it from him before he understands what he has, but it may already be too late.

title: Un Triunfo Robado
description: Dan se embarca en una aventura para superar al nuevo equipo de Peleadores Bakugan de Magnus, pero al final, ellos lo salvarán a él.

title: Corporate Buyout
description: The Cheetara Corp employee retreat gets canceled when Baron Karnon, a mysterious corporate raider, buys them out! Now Cheetara and Jan-Jan must brave the wilds of Third Earth's most dangerous jungles to find the Baron's office and demand a meeting with the man who stole their company!

title: En Suenos
description: Los sueños de Steven comienzan a transmitirse en el televisor de su dormitorio.

title: You Remind Me of Someone
description: Ben and Gwen look for the infamous Bojamboo (the Bigfoot of the South) and discover that it's actually the Forgeti, at the same time as Kevin 11, but when Ben and Kevin are blasted with the Forgeti's forgetfulness mist, they reverse roles and it's up to Gwen and Max to restore them back to normal.

title: Big Reveal
description: KO finds out who his father is.

title: The Boys Are Back in Town
description: Him brings the Rowdyruff Boys back, protecting them from the girls' feminine wiles.

title: Lion-S
description: Lion-O and the other ThunderCats are thrilled to meet a brand new Thunderian: Lion-S! She's cool, good at fighting robots and, most importantly, thinks Lion-O and his Sword of Omens are really neat and interesting! Looks like the ThunderCats have a new best friend! Maybe even, a new ThunderCat?????

title: #PowerSurge
description: When Supergirl is presumed dead after a battle with Livewire, Kara Danvers decides to reinvent herself with a new look, a new personality, and a new name, Power Girl.

title: #HuevosRevueltos
description: Gracias a la tarea de la clase de Economía Domestica, los estudiantes son emparejados y se les entrega un huevo para "cuidar" durante el fin de semana. Pero cuando la tragedia acontece huevo tras huevo, lo que debería ser una tarea fácil, ise convierte en una disparatada persecución!
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Red Action 3: Grudgement Day
description: KO and Enid attempt to prevent a mysterious power battle between Rad and Red Action.

title: Mandora's Law
description: Tygra creates a bunch of new laws for Third Earth so Mandora can finally arrest the Mutants. Unfortunately the Thundercats are really bad at following their own rules and the Mutants are really good at working around them.

title: Hurricane Dilliss
description: Things in the Wendle household are turned upside down when Mary's mom Dyllis comes to visit, butting her way into every corner of Clarence, Mary and Chad's life.

title: Get That BORFL!
description: A restful chill day for the Warriors and Princess Zange in the Royal Spa gets upended when a cute little Borfl runs amok throughout Castle Rhyboflaven, with the Warriors resorting to Magiswords to thwart the critter.

title: Except for Cooper
description: A young boy must learn to eat his spinach in order to save Uncle Grandpa and the others from a rowdy gang of evil vegetables.

title: Things That Go Plunk
description: A shy, puny member of the Bad Crowd shows up at the Cloudseeker claiming he's been kicked out of Blusterland for being nice. The Bears, leery at first, take him in despite Grumpy's suspicions that he is in cahoots with Bluster. It appears Grumpy is right - but thanks to the Care Bears, the little guy turns into a good friend with the courage to thwart Bluster's latest scheme.

title: Idiosyncratic Induction
description: On Elliott's first day at the Hive, he meets the most unusual characters on his adventure so far.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: Un Golpe de Ternura
description: Después de derrotar a Strata, Los Fantásticos se dan cuenta de que no volvieron solos, sino con un Bakugan parecido a un panda que les dará muchos problemas.

title: The Treasure Chest/A Camping We Will Go/Chopsticks/A Special Dog
description: Caillou is helping Mom clean out the attic./The family goes away for a weekend of camping in the woods./Caillou has dinner at Sarah's house and discovers new foods and a new way to eat them./Caillou and Mom meet a fascinating woman in the park.

title: The Magical Box
description: Three baby bear brothers are granted a magical box that can transport them to any place in the universe.

title: Sed de Poder
description: Axel y sus juguetes despliegan el Joyride en una batalla de "barco" a "barco" contra el Dr. Nautilus, quien ha perforado una tubería de agua para inundar las alcantarillas y se ha establecido como "Almirante Nautilus".

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Las Pesadillas
description: When Vic and Val experience a mysterious nightmare that turns deadly, they realize they must stop a sinister force from enchanting them to sleep forever.

title: Criando Bebe
description: Zoe deja a Axel a cargo del proyecto escolar, vigilando una muñeca simulador de bebés, pero cuando MadCap da vida a la muñeca, iAxel y el equipo deben detener al bebé sin dañarlo o correr el riesgo de obtener una calificación reprobatoria!

title: Freezer Burn
description: Batman and Firestorm team up to fight their respective cold villains, Mr. Freeze and Killer Frost. Complications arise when Firestorm's infatuation for the wily Ms. Frost gets the best of him.

title: Tiara Trouble
description: Bubbles' excitement over being a contestant in the Townsville Beauty, Talent and All-Around Flair pageant is ruined when Blossom and Buttercup become overbearing stage-sisters. But when a mysterious tiara causes trouble for the contestants, they realize there are bigger problems at hand.

title: The Choices
description: When a typically stressful Watterson family dinner pushes her to the edge of her sanity, Nicole starts reminiscing about the time she met Richard. Might her life have been better if she'd never stopped to talk to her future husband and taken a different path instead?

title: #LaReinaDelDrama
description: Oliver Queen debe enfrentarse al mayor rival al que jamás se haya enfrenado, Mortimer Drake, mientras Green Arrow se encuentra con un nuevo enemigo.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Thunder Road
description: When a crate containing fifty Swords of Omen lands on Third Earth, the ThunderCats rush out in the ThunderTank to find them. Unfortunately The Mutants and Mumm-Ra want those swords too so it's going to be a race to get to them! A wacky race, you might say. We won't say that, but you might.

title: Growing
description: Meet Bing and his friends… Join us and celebrate the noisy, joyful, messy reality of preschool life.

title: The Re-Run
description: When we last saw Gumball, he was hitting rewind on Rob's Universal Remote just in time to save himself from being trapped in The Void. The remote has now taken Gumball back to the beginning of that disastrous day. Armed with the knowledge of what this day has in store, he must try and stop Rob from destroying his life.

title: Luthor in Paradise
description: With the aid of Circe the Witch, Luthor travels to Paradise Island to steal an artifact that will give him god-like powers. When Superman and Batman arrive on the island to bring him back, they find that they're almost as popular with the Amazons as Luthor on this woman-only island.

title: Under Wraps
description: When Ben and Gwen are sent to a farm to learn the value of hard work, what they really learn is that an evil alien mummy has arrived on Earth.

title: Even More Shorts
description: Weird Man apprehends a dangerous foreign criminal, Belly Bag discovers a cat stuck in the RV tree, and Uncle Grandpa hosts a space exploration program on this new collection of shorts.

title: Lambporcini
description: Apple and Onion are very happy with their sweet new matching designer outfits they bought from known scam-artist Street Dog. That's until Chicken Nugget mistakes them for something they are not.

title: El Hijo de Lilly
description: iLa batalla por el destino de la Montaña Shintaro concluye!

title: Rage of the Red Lanterns
description: Chased by the Red Lanterns, Lobo seeks sanctuary with the Justice League. As the League attempts to stave off the Red Lanterns, Lobo reveals the real reason he wants shelter in the Watchtower, he wants access to a powerful space weapon being held by our heroes.

title: Animo Crackers
description: Dr. Animo from the future comes back to the present to help himself defeat Ben once and for all. (Introducing new Ben alien, Gutrot.)

title: Gnome More Mister Nice Guy
description: When the daycare gets taken over by evil gnomes, Duncan finds himself on the wrong team.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: El Misterio de la Guardiana del Tiempo
description: Cuando la Guardiana del Tiempo desaparece, Craig y sus amigos asumen la tarea de ayudar a otros niños a llegar a casa a tiempo para la cena.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Family BBQ
description: Mordecai wants to get a handshake from Margaret's dad.

title: #GatoCallejero Parte 2
description: Cuando Zee Zatara se da cuenta de que Lex Luthor desenterró un libro mágico que tiene el poder de predecir el futuro, las chicas le piden ayuda a Gatúbela para robárselo antes de que Lex comprenda lo que tiene en su poder. Pero puede que ya sea demasiado tarde...
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Prickly Pair
description: After leaving Little Homeschool, Steven has found a new hobby, plants.

title: Adrenalandia Junior
description: El equipo de Tennyson visita la versión segura de Adrenalandia, conocida como "Adrenalandia Jr", y allí terminan enfrentándose a un Kevin 11 amargado y decidido a destruir la diversión segura de todos los demás.

title: Un Comienzo Dificil
description: iLos ninja han encontrado su búsqueda! Ahora solo tienen que llegar allí, lo que implica un viaje por carretera a través del desierto de Doom, una región supuestamente habitada por un escarabajo gigante.

title: Operation Dude Rescue Part 1
description: When the male Titans are captured, it's up to Starfire and Raven to rescue them but they're going to need some extra girl power.

title: Thirst for Power
description: Axel and his toys deploy the Joyride in a "ship" to "ship" battle against Dr. Nautilus, who has punctured a water main to flood the sewers and established himself as "Admiral Nautilus."

title: El Oso Troyano
description: Cuando Axel abre una caja de regalo de suscripción que ni siquiera ordenó, el equipo encuentra sus filas divididas por un oso robótico, io la Princesa SugarSalt disfrazada!

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Que Rima Con Omnitrix?
description: En un recital de lectura de poesía, Charmcaster lee poemas de Kevin y les causa problemas mágicos a Ben y Gwen cuando produce intercambios mentales que dejan a todos confundidos acerca de quién pelea contra quién.

title: The Audition
description: The Bears audition to be the next mascot for their favorite cereal. They get so caught up in the process that their competitiveness gets the best of them.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Bonnibel Bubblegum
description: A long lost artifact causes Princess Bubblegum to harken back to the creation of the Candy Kingdom.

title: Estirado Demasiado Delgado
description: Después de que un nuevo movimiento combinado deja a Masko permanentemente flácido, Axel y el equipo deben ayudar al luchador caído a recuperarse.

title: Meteor Moves
description: Mordecai wants to finally kiss Margaret at a meteor shower.

title: The Wrinklegruff Gals
description: Sick of being the tiniest kids at their new school, the girls convince Professor Utonium to create a potion to make them older! Unfortunately, when they take too much, they become senior citizens and a prime target for Mojo Jojo!

title: El Tronco es mio
description: Cuando un niño reclama posesión del Tronco, Craig no tiene otra opción que llevarlo a juicio.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: The New Lars
description: Steven gets a new look into Lars' life.

title: Captain Craboo
description: The Bears are reunited with their pet crab, Captain Craboo. But after an unfortunate run-in with Nom Nom, the Bears may lose their pet forever.

title: The Scam
description: At Halloween show and tell, the class isn't buying Gumball's story about Gargaroth the Devourer until Carrie fakes a terrifying haunting. The kids convince the school to hire them as ghost exterminators and take their payment in Halloween candy. But when it turns out Gargaroth is real, suddenly Gumball is expected to be the town's savior.

title: Blue Ribbon Blues
description: When a famous scientist comes to the school, Blossom will stop at nothing to impress him at the Science Fair even if that means putting Townsville in danger!

title: The Shortcut
description: An unusually hot day at the Creek melts all of Kit's ice pops, so Craig helps her find a short cut to her frozen snack supplier before everyone else melts.

title: Daycare of Rock
description: After believing he's turned Chef to stone Duncan sets his sights on ultimate chaos only to discover there's no joy in victory without an adversary.

title: Borrowed
description: Richard discovers his library books have been borrowed by Master Frown and sets off on a crazed mission to return the books before they're overdue.

title: Country Club
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to rescue the golf cart from a bunch of rich people at a country club.

title: The Return
description: Ghostfreak has returned! And he has brought a Mummy, Werewolf and Frankenstein like aliens with him to help him shroud the Earth in darkness.

title: Bad Heir Day
description: Princess Zange's Autostyle Magisword is stolen and it's up to the Warriors to retrieve it so their royal leader can face her subjects without bad hair.

title: Seed No Evil/City of Clipsville
description: Seed No Evil: When a prehistoric caveman thaws out in Townsville, the girls must stop him from stealing the Mayor's seeds./City of Clipsville: The girls reminisce on their adventures in these new, never-before-seen clips!

title: Wasted True Potential
description: In the wake of the previous season's victory, the ninja have gone soft and Master Wu must remind them of who they truly are.

title: Adrenaland Jr.
description: Team Tennyson visits the safety-neutered version of Adrenaland known as "Adrenaland Jr.", only to end up facing off against a bitter Kevin 11, out to destroy everyone else's good, and safe, time.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: Me Recuerdas a Alguien
description: Ben y Gwen buscan al tristemente célebre Bojamboo (el Pie Grande del Sur) y descubren que en realidad se trata del Olvideti.

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Plastic Man Saves the World
description: Plastic Man feels shuffled off to the side as the Justice League battles Brainiac so he takes it upon himself to infiltrate the alien's ship on his own and thwart the villain's plans.

title: Wicked Shades
description: When Pizza Steve borrows Uncle Grandpa's sunglasses, he sees things in a whole new light.

title: The Great Fossil Rush
description: JP finds a fossil in the Creek which quickly causes the landscape to change.

title: Always BMO Closing
description: BMO and Ice King hit the road as door to door salesmen and stumble upon an irresistible opportunity.
